sub_title: Desk Officer at Ministry of Finance
summary: I am a civil servant and former diplomat at the Swedish Government Offices where I have just joined the Ministry of Finance. Prior to this I worked as Senior Researcher at the Chief Economist Office of PwC Netherlands. At PwC, I worked on strategic Thought Leadership publications related to energy, climate change and sustainability more broadly. I have experience of working on those topics in both developed and developing market contexts. As a diplomat for the Swedish government I was responsible for the Economic Affairs portfolio at the Swedish Embassy in Warsaw and I also worked for the Swedish Trade Council in The Hague.
